general.name: DRQv_superset
general.description:
The primary DR12Q catalog is derived from a well-defined superset of quasar targets that are documented in PÃ¢ris et al. (2015).

This webpage documents the format of the DR12Q_superset.fits file. This file contains the result of the full visual inspection of the DR12Q superset.
